</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-63_ pf-text-1"><strong>Immobilisation</strong> - Carefully support the injured limb using improvised splints or padding to prevent further movement and minimise pain. However, avoid applying direct pressure to the injury site.







































